### Kuyruga katil (kapasite dolu senaryosu)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/queue/{{eventId}}/join
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{"userId": "{{userId}}"}

### Pozisyon sorgula
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/queue/{{eventId}}/position?userId={{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Ikinci kullanici katilir
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/queue/{{eventId}}/join
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{"userId": "{{userId2}}"}

### Kuyruktan cik
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/queue/{{eventId}}/leave
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{"userId": "{{userId}}"}
